{
  "title": "CentOS 6/7使用Nux Dextop源安装VLC",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<embed id=\"xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd\" type=\"application/thunder_download_plugin\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"http://li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(179, 43, 213); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\">Nux Dextop</a><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\">是一个面对CentOS、RHEL、ScientificLinux的含有许多流行的桌面和多媒体相关的包的第三方RPM仓库（比如：Ardour，Shutter等等）。目前，Nux Dextop桌面对CentOS和RHEL 6/7可用。</span><div id=\"isForwardContent\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><div style=\"line-height: 1.7;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/1726C60872996109E79648F03745193B.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px;\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\">要在CentOS或者RHEL上启用Nux Dextop，遵循下面的步骤。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\">首先，要知道Nux Dextop被设计与EPEL仓库共存。因此，你需要在使用Nux Dexyop仓库前先<a href=\"http://xmodulo.com/2013/03/how-to-set-up-epel-repository-on-centos.html\" style=\"color: rgb(179, 43, 213);\">启用 EPEL</a>。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\">启用EPEL后，用下面的命令安装Nux Dextop仓库。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\">在 CentOS/RHEL 6.* 上:</p><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\"><li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pln\">$ sudo rpm&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"typ\">Uvh</span><span class=\"pln\">&nbsp;<a href=\"http://li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/el6/x86_64/nux-dextop-release-0-2.el6.nux.noarch.rpm\">http</a></span><span class=\"pun\"><a href=\"http://li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/el6/x86_64/nux-dextop-release-0-2.el6.nux.noarch.rpm\">:</a></span><span class=\"com\"><a href=\"http://li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/el6/x86_64/nux-dextop-release-0-2.el6.nux.noarch.rpm\">//li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/el6/x86_64/nux-dextop-release-0-2.el6.nux.noarch.rpm</a></span></li></ol><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\">在 CentOS/RHEL 7 上 :</p><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\"><li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pln\">$ sudo rpm&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"typ\">Uvh</span><span class=\"pln\">&nbsp;<a href=\"http://li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/el7/x86_64/nux-dextop-release-0-1.el7.nux.noarch.rpm\">http</a></span><span class=\"pun\"><a href=\"http://li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/el7/x86_64/nux-dextop-release-0-1.el7.nux.noarch.rpm\">:</a></span><span class=\"com\"><a href=\"http://li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/el7/x86_64/nux-dextop-release-0-1.el7.nux.noarch.rpm\">//li.nux.ro/download/nux/dextop/el7/x86_64/nux-dextop-release-0-1.el7.nux.noarch.rpm</a></span></li></ol><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\">现在验证Nux Dextop仓库是否已经成功安装：yum repolist.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\">然后，安装VLC: sudo yum -y install vlc.即可。</p></div></div>"
    }
  ]
}